WEBVTT

00:04.271 --> 00:06.705
Hey, everybody,
I'm home.

00:09.976 --> 00:12.578
- And I've got presents.
- Yes! Awesome.

00:12.579 --> 00:15.581
- Hi, dad.
- Daddy, we missed you.

00:15.582 --> 00:17.650
I love you, presents.

00:17.651 --> 00:20.186
I mean dad!

00:20.187 --> 00:22.088
Okay, so I'm doing

00:22.089 --> 00:25.024
an extermination job over
at Loony Larry's electronics.

00:25.025 --> 00:28.861
He was infested with termites,
rats and great deals!

00:28.862 --> 00:32.231
Because he's loony!

00:32.232 --> 00:35.634
Okay, for P.J.

00:35.635 --> 00:39.205
- For Teddy.
- Smart phones, awesome!

00:39.206 --> 00:41.841
- Thank you so much.
- Where's my smart phone?

00:41.842 --> 00:45.144
P.J.'s holding it. You're gonna
get it in about four years.

00:46.346 --> 00:49.615
But for you I got a
remote-control helicopter!

00:49.616 --> 00:52.284
- This is cool.
- ...That we put together ourselves.

00:52.285 --> 00:54.854
- Ruined it.
- What?

00:54.855 --> 00:56.822
I thought this would be
a fun father-son project.

00:56.823 --> 01:00.493
Okay, why don't you put it
together with your father

01:00.494 --> 01:02.762
And give me a call.

01:02.763 --> 01:05.965
And I even got

01:05.966 --> 01:08.601
A little something
for Charlie.

01:11.905 --> 01:13.606
* I'm a happy happy horse *

01:13.607 --> 01:15.040
* happy happy
happy horse *

